* Starostin, Sergei/Dybo, Anna/Mudrak, Oleg, &quot;Etymological Dictionary of the Altaic Languages&quot; (&quot;Этимологический Словарь Алтайских языков&quot;), 3 vols, Leiden and Boston 2003 

